  "description": "<p><strong>• 1 year contract (renewable)</strong></p><p><strong>• Novena</strong></p><p><strong>• Monday to Friday: 9.00am - 6.30pm</strong></p><p><strong>• Up to $5000 + End of Contract Bonus + commission + PB</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Promote & sell Life Insurance (General Insurance)</li><li>To achieve individual sales targets</li><li>To adhere to professional standards of behaviour & conduct in dealing with customers and fellow staff</li><li>To continuously think ahead and help to develop solutions to emerging problems</li><li>To continuously suggest ways in improving the team as a whole</li><li>To actively tele-market the Bank's products to customers to generate sales revenue</li><li>To call company provided leads or customers</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Period:</strong></p><ul><li>1 Year Contract (renewable)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Location:</strong></p><ul><li>Novena</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Monday – Friday (9.00am – 6.30pm)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $5000 + End of Contract Bonus + commission + PB</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Secondary School 'O' Levels – 3 Credits</li><li><strong>Must have BCP, PGI and HI Certificate</strong></li><li>Applicants must be willing to work in Novena Area</li><li>Passion and drive to launch sales career to the next level</li><li>Good Communication Skills</li><li>Self-starter, independent and possess excellent interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Comfortable with Quotas or Sales Targets</li><li>Candidates must be able to commit to Overtime if needed</li><li>Relevant sales/acquisition experience with a proven track record is a plus</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly email your detailed resume (MS Word format is preferred):</p><p><strong>faiza@successhrc.com.sg </strong>(Reg 